#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:2
#: 68be373b79824e869731fcf84a1ffcee
msgid "安信可 2.4G系列模块 FAQ"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker 2.4G Series Module FAQ"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:18
#: 960627ff87024a37b2b22552a26421c2
msgid "Si24R1芯片与nRF24L01+芯片有什么区别?"
msgstr "What is the difference between the Si24R1 chip and the nRF24L01+ chip?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:19
#: 20270a0202c14d86b5bc87463ea0be29
msgid ""
"Si24R1芯片与nRF24L01+芯片兼容，可以直接替换。SI24R1芯片的优点就是SHDN关断状态"
"的电流要小，standby-I状态的电流也要小，同时SI24R1芯片支持更大功率的输出7dBm，"
"（需要软件设置内部寄存器配置使之工作在7dBm模式），SI24R1的总的平均电流消耗要"
"比nRF24L01+的小。"
msgstr ""
"The Si24R1 chip is compatible with the nRF24L01+ chip and can be used as a "
"direct replacement. The advantages of the Si24R1 chip are lower current "
"consumption in SHDN shutdown state and lower current consumption in standby-"
"I state. At the same time, the Si24R1 chip supports a higher output power of "
"7dBm. (Software configuration of internal registers is required to make it "
"work in 7dBm mode. ) The overall average current consumption of the Si24R1 "
"is lower than that of the nRF24L01+."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:22
#: 75aa41a4d80a4f86b7851cc6261844a7
msgid "Si24R1与nRF24L01+与BK2425芯片哪一个性能比较好?"
msgstr "Which chip has better performance: Si24R1, nRF24L01+, or BK2425?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:24
#: 330344d2742e4567808154092d337ffd
msgid ""
"答：从功率上比较：Si24R1最大功率是5mV>BK2425最大功率是2.5mV>nRF24L01最大功率"
"是1mV"
msgstr ""
"A: In terms of power: Si24R1 maximum power is 5mV > BK2425 maximum power is "
"2.5mV > nRF24L01 maximum power is 1mV."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:27
#: c977272fffd94c629a4afc446932491a
msgid "NF-03跟24l01兼容吗"
msgstr "Is NF-03 compatible with 24L01?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:29
#: 11f538de9b8d4b0595fcc393b23baa97
msgid "兼容，支持多发一收"
msgstr "Compatible. It supports multiple transmitters and one receiver."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:32
#: dab34275e82749279aa460022e8aa3f3
msgid "NF-01-S这个直接用吗 ?还是需要编程"
msgstr "Can NF-01-S be used directly, or does it need programming?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:33
#: c832b9dd7a0f4f09989cffd9db24f534
msgid "需要编程,这只是一个射频芯片"
msgstr "It needs programming. This is only an RF chip."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:36
#: 0e6b49d3106943af9b1bacb9e4d262ef
msgid "NF-04与NF-02-PA 互通吗？"
msgstr "Can NF-04 communicate with NF-02-PA?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:37
#: f253c954d3f04ad788131f38c093835c
msgid "互通的"
msgstr "Yes, they can communicate with each other."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:40
#: fb46486242514c4aa207b3e5eb0485f1
msgid "NF-03可以供电电压5v吗"
msgstr "Can the NF-03 be powered with 5V?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:41
#: b869767711174c288b8da4f02aeacc5c
msgid "建议供电3V3，供电5V会烧坏芯片"
msgstr ""
"A 3.3V power supply is recommended. A 5V power supply will burn out the chip."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:44
#: 7d08ed1b79b844b69f246c2e1ca5834e
msgid "NF-04-MI模块的通信距离有多远"
msgstr "What is the communication distance of the NF-04-MI module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:45
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:70
#: a396692b83c44d3ca24f5ebbd919ef87 1bb01e305fab41c4bea599ef3e385d3f
msgid "120米"
msgstr "120m."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:48
#: 04f161e4931a4b2186614e9aeb48b6cb
msgid ""
"NF-03模块，不需要烧写程序，直接可以透传，对吗？模块本身，上电即可工作吗？"
msgstr ""
"Does the NF-03 module support transparent transmission directly without "
"programming? Does the module itself work immediately after power-on?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:49
#: 189742b4a59042059bde1a7091c20bd0
msgid "这个模块需要外接MCU，需要MCU配置寄存器"
msgstr ""
"This module requires an external MCU, and the MCU needs to configure the "
"registers."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:52
#: 46ae6abdbd744ff49e46e75ff58b3ad7
msgid "如何把NF-01-N模块改成通电即发射？怎么设置呢？"
msgstr ""
"How can I make the NF-01-N module transmit immediately after power-on? How "
"should it be configured?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:53
#: d69e4d8af4294eab96f510030f6cc614
msgid "通过设置寄存器，可以参考我们提供的51单片机的demo程序"
msgstr ""
"It can be done by setting registers. You can refer to the 51 MCU demo "
"program we provide."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:56
#: 8bb710c7b2864a6d83a5079d741fdb05
msgid "\"NF-03传送距离多远？"
msgstr "How far is the NF-03 transmission distance?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:58
#: 81a9d22068f6472098c3be2c331365b0
msgid "240m"
msgstr "240m."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:61
#: f4ca0501eb284e9fa135730eb2804965
msgid "2.4G稳定性哪款好？"
msgstr "Which 2.4G module has good stability?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:62
#: 922d9e4cc52c4a84bd96eb77836fc8b8
msgid "NF-02-PA"
msgstr "NF-02-PA."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:65
#: 4c36e88b1c0d4cf891c4befb1cbac99b
msgid "发射端si24r1，接收端是nrf24l01+，可以通信吗"
msgstr ""
"Can a transmitter using Si24R1 communicate with a receiver using nRF24L01+?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:66
#: ec1aa48fee564f4a922b702f018b9c3c
msgid "可以通信"
msgstr "Yes, they can communicate."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:69
#: f6fe1e69231b4131a23ec1135ab91038
msgid "\"NF-04多少米"
msgstr "How far is the NF-04 transmission distance?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:73
#: 1f7eec9b1a304651bebdccc841600f2f
msgid "怎么区分NF-01-N和NF-01-S"
msgstr "How to distinguish NF-01-N and NF-01-S?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:74
#: 949be420e90a41b1be3bbefe70a1f6cf
msgid "他们使用的射频芯片不一样 可以参考芯片手册"
msgstr "They use different RF chips. You can refer to the chip manuals."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:77
#: 53913866c17641639a9b314064dbaf60
msgid "这种3.3V供电的2.4G  NF-04-MI模块，能否与5V供电的单片机信号线直接连接"
msgstr ""
"Can this 3.3V-powered 2.4G NF-04-MI module be directly connected to the "
"signal lines of a 5V-powered MCU?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:78
#: 3fe92212793a429380687e06614d455b
msgid "不行,必须设计降压电路"
msgstr "No. A step-down circuit must be designed."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:81
#: fa8ffbc2954c4427ba7c7f02084d5e66
msgid "NF-03模块有没有程序的"
msgstr "Does the NF-03 module come with a program?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:82
#: 587726c45c4f4fcc904f2df3082b8c46
msgid "NF-03这款是射频芯片，所以不带程序的，通过MCU寄存器去操作"
msgstr ""
"NF-03 is an RF chip, so it does not come with a program. It is operated by "
"MCU register configuration."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:85
#: 113faf53871a4881ac90c767237c6c97
msgid "NF-01-S 这个是wifi透传吗?是走wifi协议吗?"
msgstr ""
"Is NF-01-S Wi-Fi transparent transmission? Does it use the Wi-Fi protocol?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:86
#: b3413e79f0fd49b28101c32f21ffea61
msgid "支持SPI透传,走的不是WIFI协议 ,是SPI协议"
msgstr ""
"It supports SPI transparent transmission. It does not use the Wi-Fi "
"protocol; it uses the SPI protocol."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:89
#: baba7099585940acbf7812f02a3ada5f
msgid "NF-01-S可以做AP吗。 设备跟你们的模块连，手机APP跟模块连。实现透传。"
msgstr ""
"Can NF-01-S work as an AP? Devices connect to the module, and the mobile app "
"connects to the module to implement transparent transmission."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:91
#: c71d447d5f054f9296cb45b6635d24e3
msgid "SPI协议，这个只是纯射频模块，没有AP这种概念哦"
msgstr ""
"It uses the SPI protocol. This is only a pure RF module, so there is no AP "
"concept."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:94
#: cf072f282510478b8b0fe6eb02a77b59
msgid "2.4G系列有5V供电的吗"
msgstr "Are there any 5V-powered modules in the 2.4G series?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:95
#: fe124fc63a394d76af5786b2ef2a991a
msgid "2.4G模块都是3.3V供电的，如果使用5V供电请自行设计电路进行降压"
msgstr ""
"All 2.4G modules are powered by 3.3V. If using a 5V power supply, please "
"design your own step-down circuit."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:98
#: 40173410e9ce491bad864da12dd396cb
msgid "\"有串口通信的2.4G模块吗"
msgstr "Are there 2.4G modules with serial communication?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:99
#: 3bed619abc2a4f92981cd8dc10c50687
msgid "没有，2.4g都是SPI通信的，是单2.4，不是WIFI"
msgstr ""
"No. All 2.4G modules use SPI communication. They are single 2.4G modules, "
"not Wi-Fi modules."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:102
#: c9a06945e3f34446bc8799a138c4c627
msgid "Nf-02可以做音频传输吧？"
msgstr "Can NF-02 be used for audio transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:103
#: 03633d2aecf94147ae38b09d42c1006c
msgid "不行哦"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:106
#: 9b6b56aa97984282b55d82333904d0fa
msgid "为什么叫邦定2401模块？与普通的2401模块有什么不同？"
msgstr ""
"Why is it called a bonded 2401 module? What is the difference from an "
"ordinary 2401 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:107
#: 0cafd6e587b845ce8bf128cae82c7f1f
msgid "使用的射频芯片不一样"
msgstr "The RF chip used is different."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:110
#: 7466d8dbf1fd402797736bc694880bc0
msgid "NF-02是发射器吧？接收呢"
msgstr "Is NF-02 a transmitter? What about receiver?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:111
#: 82b70918a3d74ee7ad04ada8a287c8e8
msgid "发射和接收都可以做的"
msgstr "It can be used for both ttransmitter and receiver."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:114
#: 3eb1d37dc61246e3b544896b08a0bc3d
msgid "NF-02模块的接收可以用哪些模块呢？"
msgstr "Which modules can be used as receivers for the NF-02 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:115
#: 81a76d883413407c8a10c849bbab9748
msgid "发送和接收都可以用这个，2.4G属于收发模块"
msgstr ""
"This module can be used for both transmitting and receiving. 2.4G modules "
"are transceiver modules."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:119
#: 6c1cc6c5bb8444958ea9feabaaeea5d9
msgid ""
"\"NF-02   和 NF-03  在数据在 能对接的吧？ 能不有 NF-02 做一款 跟NF-03一样的接"
"口？"
msgstr ""
"Can NF-02 and NF-03 connect with each other in terms of data? Can you make "
"an NF-02 with the same interface as NF-03?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:121
#: e67f16d548ef45f0b0e6ff1a4830105d
msgid "数据可以对接的，但是我们没有跟NF-03一样接口的NF-02"
msgstr ""
"The data can connect with each other, but we do not have an NF-02 with the "
"same interface as NF-03."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:124
#: 02274de24b0f4d689322332b795cad46
msgid "能做遥控的是那种"
msgstr "Which module can be used for remote control?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:126
#: f76020f734744e15b1d5b7985a7498b4
msgid "2.4G、WIFI都可以"
msgstr "Both 2.4G and Wi-Fi can be used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:130
#: a6f17ea13e884442a9ce32f1157d4ed9
msgid "这款2.4G  NF-03模块实际使用过程中，最大的发射功率可以配置成多少啊？"
msgstr ""
"In actual use, what is the maximum transmit power that this 2.4G NF-03 "
"module can be configured to?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:131
#: 15ebb143325d40e59ceb40d1423bcf8d
msgid "7dbm，您可以查看我们官网的芯片手册"
msgstr "7dBm. You can check the chip manual on our official website."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:134
#: ea8dbd4aa168401dad30554e4f293ae5
msgid "NF-04-MI模块需要自己往模块的芯片里面编写程序吗？"
msgstr ""
"Do I need to write programs into the chip of the NF-04-MI module myself?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:136
#: 3bc93efa7d6e463c9d652ea2b6457b59
msgid "不需要"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:139
#: 5a46aeda54924d10b5977f3321675ad4
msgid "假如100个2.4G无线模块在同一个房间里，各个模块之间的信号互相有干扰吗？"
msgstr ""
"If 100 2.4G wireless modules are in the same room, will the signals between "
"modules interfere with each other?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:140
#: 5aab9c465e3a41e7b5ff50f50916b468
msgid "不会有干扰的"
msgstr "No, there will be no interference."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:143
#: 48888494a1a24c83b57d72d3ef4a1cb9
msgid "这个NF-03是串口透传的吗？ 有多少个信道？"
msgstr ""
"Is this NF-03 a serial transparent transmission module? How many channels "
"does it have?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:145
#: aa3fd77eade54b04a8aacaeb0f499b22
msgid "不是串口透传哦,信道您可以查看芯片手册哈"
msgstr ""
"It is not serial transparent transmission. For channels, you can refer to "
"the chip manual."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:148
#: 24c91181af674ab2bbdeb8a3aea76a58
msgid "是否可以将SI24R1连接至电脑并显示接受的数据？是不是有配套的硬件模块？"
msgstr ""
"Can Si24R1 be connected to a computer and display received data? Is there a "
"supporting hardware module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:149
#: cfe23a5d03f747dbac15c897fd03c486
msgid "SI24R1模块是需要MCU去驱动才能进行使用"
msgstr "The Si24R1 module requires an MCU to drive it before it can be used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:152
#: 6bad86be7e7a4f968744e12b20727c7c
msgid ""
"NF-03模块是免开发模块，还是一定要连接mcu，如果用这个模块连接RC522射频模块，可"
"以正常工作吗"
msgstr ""
"Is the NF-03 module a development-free module, or must it be connected to an "
"MCU? If this module is connected to an RC522 RF module, can it work properly?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:153
#: 9d834576966e47aa842022b806647e4b
msgid "一定要接MCU"
msgstr "It must be connected to an MCU."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:156
#: cd5df379ab2c46ff857cef72af334cac
msgid ""
"2.4G模块 你们提供上位机端的测试工具吗？ 如果我使用你们的模块 那应该怎样测试这"
"个模块的工作情况呢"
msgstr ""
"Do you provide a PC-side test tool for 2.4G modules? If I use your module, "
"how should I test whether the module is working properly?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:158
#: 301421db83014259ae55198fd1147fc2
msgid "我们没有上位机端的测试工具，无法提供,通过MCU驱动."
msgstr ""
"We do not have a PC-side test tool and cannot provide one. It is driven "
"through an MCU."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:162
#: ea6d544d2c834914b61d8e994c77c3c8
msgid "NF-04-MI可以直接连串口透传吗？"
msgstr ""
"Can NF-04-MI be directly connected to a serial port for transparent "
"transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:164
#: 9522fd4549e14510bb10e26a24c61b82
msgid "不可以"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:167
#: 1abfb05b8cf742b8862f9a0a811e7e83
msgid "NF-02延时时间是多久"
msgstr "What is the delay time of NF-02?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:168
#: 473a9fdfc7e64834b3969146c72ab397
msgid "200ms"
msgstr "200ms."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:171
#: 24767ce6ef43493780b2c5ba0377784a
msgid "Nf-03这个程序和NRF24L01的通用吗"
msgstr "Is the program for NF-03 compatible with NRF24L01?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:172
#: fbf0862746554feca6f1e503dd3376d3
msgid "通用"
msgstr "Yes, compatible."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:176
#: 62c42f61dc9049f9ace582370e37cef6
msgid ""
"NF-04-MI手册上说能传输120米，实际测试10米不到，有办法提高通讯距离吗 ？如果布"
"线好的话，能传输多远呢，速度最低的情况下，你们测试试过吗"
msgstr ""
"The NF-04-MI manual says it can transmit 120 meters, but the actual test is "
"less than 10 meters. Is there any way to improve the communication distance? "
"If the wiring is good, how far can it transmit? Have you tested it at the "
"lowest speed?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:178
#: d0fb62db286f44bdbe210093e84b9d94
msgid ""
"改善天线区域的布线。NF-04-MI这个不能传远距离的，如果需要传远距离推荐使用"
"NF-03，NF-03能传输175米，NF-04-MI只能传30米"
msgstr ""
"Improve the wiring in the antenna area. NF-04-MI is not suitable for long-"
"distance transmission. If long-distance transmission is required, NF-03 is "
"recommended. NF-03 can transmit 175 meters, while NF-04-MI can only transmit "
"30 meters."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:181
#: 4c144ebad59c44a281467c4068041ca8
msgid "nrf24L01可以和BK2425通讯对吧"
msgstr "Can nRF24L01 communicate with BK2425?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:183
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:236
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:241
#: fc043d769f5d4fb78909ad8533711183 c44e5a12af5549b0ab92331f3bae29ae
#: ca439c34d0ec4b389c93ce9e9a868fbf
msgid "可以的"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:186
#: 470c704136c64f639225f7fbdddad617
msgid "NF-03，想改用ipx胶棒天线，要怎么焊接？"
msgstr ""
"For NF-03, if I want to use an IPEX rubber antenna instead, how should I "
"solder it?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:187
#: 7e6729b7550748a1a643ab9fc7bf5ffe
msgid "这个无法改用哦，上面没有预留IPEX接口，只能使用板载天线"
msgstr ""
"This cannot be changed. There is no reserved IPEX interface on it, so only "
"the onboard antenna can be used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:190
#: 35fd34aa5d434d648f3d813bb97e5a79
msgid "2.4G模块是烧录好程序的吗？透传使用"
msgstr ""
"Are 2.4G modules pre-programmed? Can they be used for transparent "
"transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:191
#: 61667e4c982044d880a16676397d4fd1
msgid "不能透传，NF-03只是一个射频模块，程序是已经固化好的"
msgstr ""
"They cannot be used for transparent transmission. NF-03 is only an RF "
"module, and the program is already solidified."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:194
#: e7578bc81a4a4972aab853110e37e81b
msgid "NF-02-PA要不要焊电容？"
msgstr "Does NF-02-PA require soldering a capacitor?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:195
#: 2819a1f4d5e346bea27f2889a6156249
msgid "不需要焊电容"
msgstr "No capacitor needs to be soldered."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:198
#: 9935c2108209490698c7016b7a4ecfe5
msgid "NRF24L01,一收多发，最多可以挂几个通信？"
msgstr ""
"For NRF24L01, in one-receiver-multiple-transmitters mode, how many devices "
"can communicate at most?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:199
#: 82937170f7044fe1bd05aa2d5db77d8c
msgid "6个，2.4G模块是通过SPI协议操作相关的寄存器值来传数据的"
msgstr ""
"6, the 2.4G module transmits data by operating related register values "
"through the SPI protocol."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:203
#: 484fd65e2786459badc2db8272f936bb
msgid "NF-02-PE这个模块，发射时电流峰值是多少"
msgstr "What is the peak current of the NF-02-PE module during transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:204
#: 9f596e668fc645c8b70056a403625f22
msgid "250mA"
msgstr "250mA."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:207
#: 1b5031911e8048b99b0aac75995c540b
msgid "NF-01-N看可以提供stm32F103c8t6的例程，在哪里可以下载"
msgstr "Where can I download the STM32F103C8T6 example for NF-01-N?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:209
#: 35c797066ccd41a4bde69fd00d5dc683
msgid "2.4G的demo程序没有STM32的，都是51单片机的demo程序，您可以自己进行移植"
msgstr ""
"There is no STM32 demo program for 2.4G modules. Only 51 MCU demo programs "
"are available. You can port it yourself."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:213
#: 4661611a029a4c92bc7deffd9323c63c
msgid "这个NF-04模块支持透传的"
msgstr "Does this NF-04 module support transparent transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:214
#: 0342bf1a94f44c78acaf2c976d775176
msgid "支持"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:217
#: 5d9fc3c5870d4c258ec073be0424374c
msgid ""
"NF-02怎么用电脑驱动它收发信号？需要哪些工具之类的？对它的配置，只是对里面射频"
"芯片的操作吗"
msgstr ""
"How can I use a computer to drive NF-02 to transmite and receive signals? "
"What tools are required? Is its configuration only about operating the RF "
"chip inside?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:219
#: 00999bdd1e6b440db760737fafec4e73
msgid ""
"必须搭配单片机使用。这边都是接单片机的，当然也可以接支持SPI的设备，但是必须对"
"里面射频芯片进行操作"
msgstr ""
"It must be used with an MCU. We usually connect it to an MCU. Of course, it "
"can also be connected to devices that support SPI, but the internal RF chip "
"must be operated."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:222
#: 66f3d956820749d8b41b4029396a8436
msgid "NF-03怎么检测他有没有发送出去"
msgstr "How can NF-03 detect whether it has transmitted successfully?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:224
#: e729cb559db141a5b9f9eef2ff67eb4e
msgid ""
"芯片手册上有一个状态寄存器 ，可以通过该寄存器进行检测，具体您可以查看这边提供"
"的代码和芯片手册"
msgstr ""
"There is a status register in the chip manual. You can detect it through "
"this register. For details, please refer to the code and chip manual we "
"provide."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:227
#: 6b54de8bdf36400fb3cdfb5477cf6518
msgid "NF-02用1M的空中速率，距离能到多少"
msgstr "How far can NF-02 reach at an air data rate of 1M?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:228
#: 46416c494d58490d9857450044c51274
msgid "1000米"
msgstr "1000m."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:231
#: 5a7123ab168b449a9cb8cd82a304f22a
msgid "金属外壳对距离有没有影响"
msgstr "Does a metal enclosure affect the distance?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:232
#: ca893dcb29764088b580db25651df3aa
msgid "会有影响，金属外壳会吸收天线辐射"
msgstr "Yes, it does. A metal enclosure will absorb antenna radiation."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:235
#: ee8db78f26974bfab6e02dd27d5eeaf5
msgid "\"NF-03可以直接替换nrf24L01吗？"
msgstr "Can NF-03 directly replace nRF24L01?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:239
#: 799ca91ad02f40c28062b2e16630fca9
msgid "NF-03是否可稳定工作在2M传输？"
msgstr "Can NF-03 work stably at 2M transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:244
#: 3092c5aa9c764a8abf86944b161dd418
msgid "NF-01-S怎么接温湿传感？"
msgstr "How does NF-01-S connect to a temperature and humidity sensor?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:245
#: 9c354120f9a34721bf4db7263a047737
msgid "外接一个MCU，MCU上接温湿度传感器"
msgstr ""
"Connect an external MCU, and connect the temperature and humidity sensor to "
"the MCU."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:248
#: 2c7bddc028fc47a2b3af868de980ae54
msgid "NF-02若希望工作在2Mbps，可工作在什么距离？"
msgstr "If NF-02 is expected to work at 2Mbps, what distance can it support?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:249
#: 76bf36aa24104c6b92b82aff9b256156
msgid "0-500米左右"
msgstr "About 0–500m."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:252
#: d542b3ac8ef0408cb2a61619958ebcc4
msgid "Si24R1与NRF24L01+的程序能否兼容，如果不兼容，需要修改哪些参数?"
msgstr ""
"Can the programs of Si24R1 and NRF24L01+ be compatible? If not, which "
"parameters need to be modified?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:253
#: 3221e6e8b284444cadb7b29b5244a3a5
msgid "不兼容，建议使用各自的驱动demo"
msgstr ""
"They are not compatible. It is recommended to use their respective driver "
"demos."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:256
#: 85d0b3eaff8a47f99b839c903fb5d79f
msgid "是否有STM32系列的示例提供？"
msgstr "Are STM32 series examples provided?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:257
#: 8b45f47b30f041db8f382a3728e82d6a
msgid "没有，只有STC51单片机的驱动程序，可以参考该程序逻辑"
msgstr ""
"No. Only the driver program for STC51 MCU is available. You can refer to the "
"logic of that program."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:260
#: 7b16343985754d28a7dca43bfa5d882e
msgid "NF-03模组能否实现一个主机配20个从机的方案？"
msgstr ""
"Can the NF-03 module implement a solution with one master and 20 slaves?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:261
#: 233ad4ea58ab4f209179868606e33455
msgid "可以，该功能主要用MCU写的应用决定。"
msgstr ""
"Yes. This function is mainly determined by the application written on the "
"MCU."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:264
#: 26615bb9fac64b9fafa7e68985f45f0a
msgid "2.4G模块在1M和2M模式下，频偏为多少"
msgstr "What is the frequency offset of the 2.4G module in 1M and 2M modes?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:265
#: 9e1b03c99fc54b41af492acbfb42d0ad
msgid "频偏为+-20ppm"
msgstr "The frequency offset is ±20 ppm."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:268
#: 883ac83351d549ac8a3aba5495d4d5aa
msgid "NF-03与NF-05软硬件兼容吗"
msgstr "Are NF-03 and NF-05 compatible in software and hardware?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:269
#: dbe02104d11f4a698a018c29a8193402
msgid "03和05只是硬件封装兼容，软件由于芯片不同需要修改相关驱动"
msgstr ""
"NF-03 and NF-05 are only compatible in hardware package. Since the chips are "
"different, the relevant software drivers need to be modified."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:272
#: 856f0a8cc7b442f382b94569f79aa0e1
msgid "请问Si24R1型号的2.4G模组是否有自动跳频功能？"
msgstr ""
"Does the Si24R1 2.4G module have an automatic frequency hopping function?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:273
#: bbb000e677424724b4bfd42fe52b3d64
msgid "没有"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:276
#: f4348135512d47968a082fdc72f55e10
msgid "请问NF-01-S模组的驱动有STM32版本的么？"
msgstr "Is there an STM32 version driver for the NF-01-S module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:277
#: 0ab17fa570a54c6a9221d7946d69844c
msgid "没有，目前只有官网上的驱动，51单片机驱动的；"
msgstr ""
"No. Currently, only the driver on the official website is available, which "
"is a 51 MCU driver."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:282
#: 23117a76905a4e54b1c1f02ca0811532
msgid "2.4G模块带自动重发不"
msgstr "Does the 2.4G module support automatic retransmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:283
#: 526b858412fb4a9e85d741bc136103a1
msgid "带，具体查看寄存器手册"
msgstr "Yes. For details, please refer to the register manual."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:286
#: 98cf897f21834900b732e5a30e952a3c
msgid "请问NF-05-S模块的flash有多大？"
msgstr "How large is the flash of the NF-05-S module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:287
#: d3458dc1eb8f49d5b10040e26ffbb98e
msgid "该模块不带MCU；"
msgstr "This module does not include an MCU."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:290
#: 72bc4f4a4dea490992aadae025455f9d
msgid "NF-05模块支持多发一收吗"
msgstr "Does the NF-05 module support multiple transmitters and one receiver?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:291
#: 1ca0a449029f4ae9bd7582f0278bb0fd
msgid "支持，具体可以从芯片手册上查询相关寄存器参数配置"
msgstr ""
"Yes. You can check the relevant register parameter configuration in the chip "
"manual."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:294
#: ad351e0e5c9c44588dc0f9988ad1f213
msgid "请问SI24R1国产芯片模组NF-03是否支持多通一？"
msgstr ""
"Does the Si24R1 domestic chip module NF-03 support multiple transmitters and "
"one receiver?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:295
#: e26fa395bace4e86afd6d0db4e83e592
msgid "需做好时间分配，模组只有一个通道用于收发；"
msgstr ""
"Time allocation must be handled properly. The module has only one channel "
"for receiving and transmitting."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:298
#: e5b0d8b3b78f413cbab267e74318b862
msgid "NF-02-PA模块怎样才能勾达到2Mbps的传输速率"
msgstr "How can the NF-02-PA module reach a transmission rate of 2Mbps?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:299
#: 2f165e03644d4feebba3d561b7f356b3
msgid "通过SPI读写相关寄存器进行操作"
msgstr "Operate it by reading and writing the relevant registers through SPI."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:302
#: 07254ff21e13433b9f5ec6e5fe8ac39b
msgid "请问Si25R1模块是否有一个固定的物理地址？如何区分模组？"
msgstr ""
"Does the Si25R1 module have a fixed physical address? How can modules be "
"distinguished?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:303
#: 2083e696b8a94359a3d596e93a114f05
msgid "没有物理地址，需在MCU上面做区分；"
msgstr ""
"There is no physical address. Distinction needs to be implemented on the MCU."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:306
#: 54a87b8d0daa4a73baf173646ee164aa
msgid "2.4G模块经常发送会一直显示达到最大重发次数的问题，该如何解决"
msgstr ""
"The 2.4G module often keeps showing that it has reached the maximum number "
"of retransmissions when transmitting. How can this be solved?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:307
#: cbca60cc85324e14856d3ad63deaf28c
msgid "检查下是否有清除TX_DS或MAX_RT中断"
msgstr "Check whether the TX_DS or MAX_RT interrupt has been cleared."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:310
#: fe320b8a640f49ac85c70a612b0f163a
msgid "纯2.4G模组支持重新烧写代码吗"
msgstr "Does a pure 2.4G module support re-flashing code?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:311
#: 79b1c292967e4cd5a9fd9a85005c0d05
msgid "不支持，该模组属于纯射频模组，出厂已固化程序，不可重新烧写"
msgstr ""
"No. This module is a pure RF module. The factory program has been solidified "
"and cannot be re-flashed."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:314
#: 33c58ec57dd74e738660aa787b071cf0
msgid "NF-01-S模组射频信号可以穿透塑料外壳吗"
msgstr "Can the RF signal of the NF-01-S module penetrate a plastic enclosure?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:315
#: fbfca2ba43924706a224eb1a05784bc5
msgid "模组射频信号可以穿透塑料外壳"
msgstr "The RF signal of the module can penetrate a plastic enclosure."
